title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 4
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Rico is ice cold and Big Cat is red hot putting him in the lead for the Pat Hill Trophy. Meanwhile, Dave looks to make some noise this week with his biggest card of the year!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
